      "text": "1. wallet.data.requested   api-gateway → data-search\n2. wallet.data.cached      data-search → process-data-ia\n                                                  data-indexing\n3. wallet.score.calculated process-data-ia → api-gateway\n                                                       data-indexing\n4. wallet.score.failed     process-data-ia → api-gateway\n5. user.analysis.consumed  api-gateway → users",
